'''Etna''' is a [[city]] in the [[Scott Valley]] area of [[Siskiyou County, California|Siskiyou County]], [[California]], [[United States]]. The population was 737 at the [[2010 United States Census|2010 census]], down from 781 at the [[2000 United States Census|2000 census]].
